name: Air Algérie A330-202 [7T-VJY] Taxi and Takeoff from Montréal-Trudeau ᴴᴰ
description:
Yet another new airline for me! Air Algérie, the national airline of Algeria, operates several flights into Montreal, its only North American destination. Here we have one of said flights taxiing and taking off runway 24R, with some great engine sound. Enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
